    <item>
      <title>KKR 拟发行 20 亿美元债务融资方案，用于收购 Instructure Acstructure</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/morgan-stanley-leads-2-billion-debt-financing-for-kkr-s-instructure-m-a</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，由摩根士丹利牵头的一个财团将提供约 20 亿美元的债务方案，以帮助 KKR &amp; Co. 收购教育软件提供商 Instructure Holdings Inc.。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/morgan-stanley-leads-2-billion-debt-financing-for-kkr-s-instructure-m-a</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 20:23:07 GMT</pubDate>
