    <item>
      <title>纽约养老基金向美光施压，要求其达成工会协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/new-york-s-260-billion-pension-fund-pressures-micron-to-make-union-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约 2600 亿美元的养老基金正在敦促美光科技公司采取全球劳工中立政策，这将为该公司芯片工厂的工人组建和加入工会铺平道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/new-york-s-260-billion-pension-fund-pressures-micron-to-make-union-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 20:20:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>电子游戏演员将罢工，寻求与人工智能相关的保护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/video-game-actors-to-go-on-strike-seek-ai-related-protections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于未能就行业内人工智能的使用达成一致，电子游戏配音演员将于周五凌晨 12:01 开始罢工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/video-game-actors-to-go-on-strike-seek-ai-related-protections</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 20:15:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
